      "representation": "view",
      "value": "<p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224201/RenderMan_LAMA_GumBall.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330612379&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224201/RenderMan_LAMA_GumBall.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330612379&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224216\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_LAMA_GumBall.jpg\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224201\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"34a232e7-1964-4912-a3cf-2272a12f2d91\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><p>This pattern supports and simplifies common metallic specular workflows from texturing applications such as Substance Painter, Substance Designer and Mari<br/><br/><span style=\"font-weight: 600;letter-spacing: -0.003em;\">Base Color</span></p><p>Input for your Base color PBR map</p><h4 id=\"PxrMetallicWorkflow-Metallic\">Metallic</h4><p>Input for your Metallic PBR map</p><h4 id=\"PxrMetallicWorkflow-Specular\">Specular</h4><p>Specular texture input. The default 0.5 value corresponds to an index of refraction of 1.5</p><p><br/></p><p>An example of how to connect your PBR Metallic maps into a PxrSurface.  You can also use the PxrMetallicWorklow node with Lama nodes too !</p><p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224201/RenderMan_PxrMetallicWorkflow.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330612378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/542224201/RenderMan_PxrMetallicWorkflow.JPG?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1754330612378&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"542224213\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"RenderMan_PxrMetallicWorkflow.JPG\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/jpeg\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"542224201\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"1\" data-media-id=\"1323d26f-65e0-4dab-8a8d-70322bdceaa7\" data-media-type=\"file\"></span></p><div class=\"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-information conf-macro output-block\" data-hasbody=\"true\" data-macro-id=\"d6ec481a-17e2-4a50-9a66-c4e7119d26da\" data-macro-name=\"info\"><p class=\"title\">Same in all DCCs</p><span class=\"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-information-macro-icon\"> </span><div class=\"confluence-information-macro-body\">This workflow is the same whether your working in Maya / Katana / Houdini or Blender.</div></div>"
    }
